The '''Egg''' and the '''Brown Egg''' are [[:Category:Animal Products|animal products]]  obtained from White, Brown, or Blue [[Chicken]]s.  [[Marnie]] may also gift you 12 eggs at the [[Feast of the Winter Star]].  

Eggs can be hatched in an [[incubator]], which comes with a Big or Deluxe [[Coop]]. 

