==Tailoring==
Egg is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Plain Overalls]].  [[File:Shirt216.png|24px]]

==Quests==
*An Egg may be randomly requested during any season at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|150}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points. This will only be requested if you own a White Chicken, Brown Chicken, or Duck. Owning a Duck will result in a chicken egg being requested.

